quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  78,1,"About what are they asking one another?"
  78,2,"Is it about the awesome tiding"
  78,3,"that they are in utter disagreement?"{1},footnotes:1:1
  78,4,"No indeed; soon will they come to know;"{1}{2},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2
  78,5,"again, no indeed; soon will they come to know."
  78,6,"Have We not spread the earth like a bed,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  78,7,"and fixed the mountains like pegs,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  78,8,"and created you in pairs (as men and women),"{1},footnotes:1:1
  78,9,"and made your sleep a means of repose,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  78,10,"and made the night a covering,"